oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Aerial view of Vanderbilt University area, 1961 March 16
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An aerial view of the Vanderbilt University campus area and surrounding acreage, March 16th, 1961. The Vanderbilt Stadium at Dudley Field is pictured and other landmarks, as well as residences in the neighborhood. The central business district of downtown Nashville is pictured in the distance. Forms part of Record Group 412, Photographs Collection. 1 photograph negative : b & w ; 4 x 5 in.
